          "range": "4080-4106",
          "rangeStart": 4080,
          "rangeEnd": 4106,
          "markText": "军是宋代的行政区域，一个军等于一个州或府，直辖于路。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1751359499,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-01 16:44:59",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106031&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4080&rangeEnd=4106",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/650324e0813ab8febg011aed?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4080&rangeEnd=4106"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300106031_7_3030-3069",
          "range": "3030-3069",
          "rangeStart": 3030,
          "rangeEnd": 3069,
          "markText": "宋代的路最初是为征收赋税转运漕粮而分的区域，后来逐渐带有行政区划和军区的性质。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1751359409,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-01 16:43:29",
